24 &#8211; Real-time video streaming from vehicle &#8211; S. RIMAC-DRLJE &#8211; Tomislav Lugarić 

25 &#8211; Telemetry data compression algorithms – J. JOB &#8211; Tomislav Lugarić 

26 &#8211; On-demand high resolution telemetry sampling – Ž. HOCENSKI &#8211; Tomislav Lugarić 

27 &#8211; In-vehicle timeseries data storage &#8211; I. LUKIĆ &#8211; Tomislav Lugarić 

28 &#8211; OTA update &#8211; J. BALEN &#8211; Tomislav Lugarić 

